# The isolated install for the in-process competitor libs (hono/elysia/fastify/
# find-my-way). Lives outside the root bun workspace so it never touches the root
# bun.lock; recreated with `bun install` inside benchmarks/.
node_modules/
bun.lock

# Competitor apps install on demand (CI / local). Their installs and lockfiles
# are not part of the monorepo's bun workspace and must not be committed.
apps/*/node_modules/
apps/*/package-lock.json
apps/*/.next/
apps/*/build/
apps/*/dist/
apps/*/.svelte-kit/

# The real-server report is one machine's one run — regenerated by driver/run.ts,
# never committed (same rule as @lesto/bench's results.json). The in-process
# COMPARISON.md IS committed as an illustrative sample, like @lesto/bench's RESULTS.md.
RESULTS.md
